===Adjective===
'''funtastic'''
#A [[source]] of [[amusement]] so [[fun]] that one could consider it [[fantastic]] 
#[[Enjoyment]] or [[amusement]] to the point of being [[fantastic]]

===Examples===
#"I say, old chap, that day at the races was '''funtastic'''."
#"But mom!  Can't I go to the fair?  The others say it will be '''funtastic'''!"
#"My God!  That is one '''funtastic''' rifle you bought."